{"type":null,"faqId":43420,"title":"手机触摸屏会自动跳屏或自动打开软件，该怎么办？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1．如果手机是在充电或者通过数据线连接电脑的情况下屏幕出现自动跳屏，先确认是否因为电压不够稳定造成，以及数据线和充电器是否为原装适配。充电电压过大会对触摸屏造成干扰，触摸屏会以为有人在触摸，所以充电或连接电脑请使用原装的华为充电器和数据线。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">步骤阅读</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 手机连接上WLAN，点击手机上的“设置 &gt; 系统更新 &gt; 检查更新查”看是否有更新系统的提示，如有提示，将手机系统升级到最新版试试。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":134,"faqType":"硬件与外观","useful":0,"unUseful":1,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"8921","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Hardware-Appearance","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442398845000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10","visitedTimes":45,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"触屏,跳屏,自动打开,软件","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}